<h2><a href="/en/theme_confederation.html">Confederation</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_confederation.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_government.html">Responsible Government</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_government.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_macdonald.html">Sir John A. Macdonald</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_macdonald.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_riviere_rouge.html">From the Red River Settlement to Manitoba (1812–70)</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_riviere_rouge.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_laurier.html">Sir Wilfrid Laurier</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_laurier.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_cartier.html">Sir George-Étienne Cartier</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_cartier.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_sports.html">Sports</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_sports.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_fenians.html">The Fenians</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_fenians.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_women.html">Women in the DCB/DBC</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_women.html?p=2">Winning the Right to Vote</a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_conferences_1864.html">The Charlottetown and Quebec Conferences of 1864</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_conferences_1864.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_essays.html">Introductory Essays of the DCB/DBC</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_essays.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_acadians.html">The Acadians</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_acadians.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/article/explorers">For Educators</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/article/explorers">Exploring the Explorers</a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_1812.html">The War of 1812&nbsp;</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_1812.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_wartime_pms.html">Canada’s Wartime Prime Ministers</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_wartime_pms.html"></a></p><h2><a href="/en/theme_first_world_war.html">The First World War</a></h2><p class="sidebar"><a href="/en/theme_first_world_war.html"></a></p></article><article id="sidenav-bottom" class="nav-left-red"><ul><li><a class="navtop" href="javascript:void(0)" title="">Back to top</a></li></ul></article></section> <!-- #left -->
